Package: ggwindrose
Title: Wind Rose Geom for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ousmane", "Ouedraogo", , "oousmane@proton.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extends 'ggplot2' with a wind rose geom that bins wind
    direction and speed observations into a direction-by-speed frequency
    table using a custom Stat/Geom pair. Coordinate, scale, and theme
    helpers produce publication-ready wind roses following meteorological
    conventions (North at top, clockwise rotation). A utility function
    computes calm-wind percentages and a custom guide renders them as a
    footer below the legend colour boxes.
